Bootstrap： 
       dropdown： 
             means： 
            use the dropdown plugin you can set assembly such as nav , title , pills-menu,button  add the dropdown menu.
             
             step: 
              @1； 
              by add  the attr : data-toogle="dropdown"  to set .
              Code: 
               <div class="dropdown">
                    <a data-toggle="dropdown" href="#">下拉菜单（Dropdown）触发器</a>
                      <ul class="dropdown-menu" role="menu" aria-labelledby="dLabel">
    ...
                      </ul>
               </div>
               
               
               
               
               Or : 
               use javascript: 
               COde:
                $(function(){
      $(".dropdown-toggle").dropdown('toggle');
      }); 
         
